ğŸ”¹ Shortcut Formula (Very Useful)

If numbers are:

a, a+d, a+2d, a+3d (AP)

Mean = Middle value (if even, average of two middle values)

ğŸ”¹ B. MEDIAN

Median = Middle value after arranging data in order

ğŸ”¹ Example 2

Find median of: 8, 3, 10, 5, 6

Arrange: 3, 5, 6, 8, 10

Middle = 6

If even numbers:

Example: 2, 4, 6, 8

Median = (4 + 6)/2 = 5

ğŸ”¹ C. MODE

Mode = Most frequently occurring value

ğŸ”¹ Example 3

2, 3, 3, 4, 5, 3

Mode = 3

